  "reference_number": "CTI0047",
  "remarks": "\nMusa Muhammad Salim Dudin is an involved person under the Counter-Terrorism (International Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 in that he: 1) is or has been a member of or associated with Hamas who is or has been involved in terrorist activity; and 2) has been involved in terrorist activity, including the supply of weapons to Hamas, a proscribed terrorist organisation, for the purposes of terrorism, in or around 1992. \n",
